<HEAD>US-Soviet Medical Research Agreement Signed</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Top health officials of the United States and
Soviet Union have signed an agreement in Moscow expanding areas of
cooperation in medical research, it was announced here.
   The so-called summary memorandum signed Friday recognizes 11
